 <span class="image">
    <img src="http://emergingindiebands.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Secret-Club-garage-rock-from-the-USA.jpg" alt="Club secret" style="width: 70%; max-width: 80%; position: relative; top: 10px; bottom: 150px; left: 20%; right: 50%">
  </span>
